<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Write lots of reviews, post them where someone will see them and publishers will start hurling books at you. Then you can share my agony of turning gr<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Write lots of reviews, post them where someone will see them and publishers will start hurling books at you. Then you can share my agony of turning great books down all the time because there just isn't enough time in the world to read everything that's offered. Like others have said, Netgalley is a great place to start (but you'll be accepted for more and better books the more you review).<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
