  <span id="freeText9437981944356531688" style="display:none">What an absolute little treasure of a book! I could not put it down and read it in one totally enjoyable afternoon. I have already read a couple of this author's better known works and enjoyed them but this one was so short yet so packed full of mystery, fantasy and a touch of horror. <br />Imagine a fabulous mansion which appears only once every nine years and two horrific vampire like residents who live forever by consuming human souls. Then follow the stories of each of those souls as they are tempted in and reach their really nasty ends.<br />A clever, almost perfect little piece of entertainment. Loved it:) </span>
