<span id="freeTextContainer3255416971835155558"><b>Trust no one........DO NOT go down the alley........DO NOT pass though the gate, and NEVER enter SLADE HOUSE for you may NEVER leave.............</b><p><u>SUPER WEIRD</u> and filled with the mysterious, this twisty haunted house tale makes for a great Halloween read! The unique format of the individual, but related stories combined with the various &quot;tricks&quot; and &quot;treats&quot; of the evil presence kept me guessing between what was real and what was imaginary.</p><p>This is my first David Mitchell novel, but NOT my last.</p></span>
  <span id="freeText3255416971835155558" style="display:none"><b>Trust no one........DO NOT go down the alley........DO NOT pass though the gate, and NEVER enter SLADE HOUSE for you may NEVER leave.............</b><p><u>SUPER WEIRD</u> and filled with the mysterious, this twisty haunted house tale makes for a great Halloween read! The unique format of the individual, but related stories combined with the various "tricks" and "treats" of the evil presence kept me guessing between what was real and what was imaginary.</p><p>This is my first David Mitchell novel, but NOT my last.</p></span>
